-- Understand the 3 models:  
##### CIA (Confidentiality, Integrity, Availability)
##### AAA (Authenticatino, Authorization, Accounting)
##### Non-repudiation (cant deny)

Confidentiailty : how can you keep your aws account confidential, you dont want it open to the world
##### AWS Services:  IAM, MFA
Integrity :
##### Certificate Manager - verifies the organization you are connecting with says who it is, otherwise wouldnt have had SSL certificates issud
##### IAM, Bucket Policies - control the integrity of S3 buckets (for example)
Availability
##### Auto-Scaling, Multi AZ

-- AAA Model
##### Authentication - IAM
##### Authorization - Policies
##### Accounting - Cloudtrail
